# Project Overview

Use this page for durable project context that several local files can reference
while still syncing one Notion page per `.nmd` file.

## Current Focus

- Keep the local workspace organized by folder.
- Run recursive `status` before broad pushes.
- Let duplicate page-id preflight catch accidental copies before mutation.
